    <string name="info_title">About Pebbels</string>
    <string name="info_hello">Hi, I\'m Pebbels</string>
    <string name="info_dates">March 28, 2014 – May 25, 2026 †</string>
    <string name="info_story1">This app was created for Pebbels — a French Bulldog who suffered from an insulinoma, an insulin-producing tumor of the pancreas. For many months, a CGM sensor and this app helped keep an eye on her blood sugar around the clock — and probably prevented several nighttime crises.</string>
    <string name="info_story2">What her illness cost in experience and hard lessons should now help other dogs and their people — so that no one has to walk this path alone.</string>
    <string name="info_more">LEARN MORE</string>
    <string name="info_more_text">Pebbels\' whole story, honest experiences with insulinoma, glucose charts, nutrition, emergency knowledge and sensor tips:</string>
    <string name="info_open_website">Open website</string>
    <string name="info_free">Free, ad-free, no data collection.</string>

